<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>وَإِنْ خِفْتُمْ أَلَّا تُقْسِطُوا فِي الْيَتَامَى ٣ ٣/ ٢٩٧<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
